column5: Hi Fella-Addicts!  I haven't been around to the area yet - but does anyone know if the marina ice has melted? I'm planning to head down April 8th... just checking if anyone has passed by to see what the ice-status is on the Marina...  Thanks in Advance, A2F (Rob)
Nope. There are guys still out from the old outflow icefishing. Can't say how much ice is there, or the quality, but there is no open water yet.
Talk to us again in May.Over 30"'s still in there and calling for minus temps at night this week.It may never leave lol.

I haven't been around to the area yet - but does anyone know if the marina ice has melted? Thanks in Advance,   http://www.barrie.ca/City%20Hall/Webcams/Pages/default.aspx Now you can see for yourself..
I didn't measure when we where fishing the general area last weekend.  Had to be 2' left though.  X2 on fisherman!
Just got off the ice. Yes I was fishing the marina. I was fishing Fishermans favorite dock. STUPID FISH.   2FT OF ICE,CRAPPIE WALKING
Hope you marked the hole...  Dont eat the yellow snow.
